Blackheart laughed under his breath, "This is past earth Darangel, you know 
how important it is. Our job here is not to change the past like the blasted 
megatron did. We like our future, could you please make a final run through 
of the shields and weapons, make sure theyre all 100% not thatd id expect 
anything less of the Spark detsroyer."
